{"build_type":"library","module_name":"dequeue-chunk-from-reclaim-ring","package_name":"dequeue-chunk-from-reclaim-ring","description":"Lock-free MPMC reclaim-ring dequeue (count give-back for empty, no CAS). c=fetch_add(count,-1); if c<=0 give it back and return 0 (empty -> caller falls through to the atomic cursor bump). Else pos=fetch_add(deq,+1), wait the producer's publish (seq==pos+1), read the chunk ptr, release the slot (seq=pos+capacity). Returns the chunk base or 0.","function_definitions":{"dequeue-chunk-from-reclaim-ring":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"ring_base","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"one","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":1},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"negone","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":-1},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"mask","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":4095},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s24","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":24},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s16","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":16},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"eight","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":8},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"sixteen16","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":16},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"cap","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":4096},{"instruction_type":"atomic_fetch_add","address":"ring_base